		</Group>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻影以不规则的攻击连招使用阔剑进行攻击，一共有2种：<br/>左扫一圈，造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害；<br/>纵劈一下，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">90%</span><span>伤害；<br/>此外，每次挥剑都会在原地留下停滞的裂缝，片刻后崩裂造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻影旋转阔剑并丢出，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害；<br/>该技能容易与普攻形成连招。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="437" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">低于<span color="#ffdfbf">75%</span><span>生命值时，幻影消失，并在场地留下2处涡眼，涡眼带有</span><span textDecoration="underline">星锥</span><span>，其中的涡眼将慢慢变大，16s后变为</span><span color="#ffacff">幻形牙兽·雷</span><span>，其立即扫尾并产生剑气，两者均造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>牙兽攻击力的伤害。<br/>(牙兽的攻击力约</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3510</span><span>(</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3.7854B2</span><span>))</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="441" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">低于<span color="#ffdfbf">50%</span><span>生命值时，幻影消失，并在场地留下3处星隙，其将锁定玩家，6s后变为鲸刺并依次发射，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>尖刺攻击力的伤害。低于</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25%</span><span>生命值时将与「噬涡黑牙」一起施放，且出现4处星隙。<br/>(鲸刺的攻击力约</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1003</span><span>(</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1.0816B2</span><span>))</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻影闪现，并在传送门后出现，进行挥剑并产生剑气，挥剑造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害，剑气造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。通常在</span><span color="#ffdfbf">现身时</span><span>施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻影自身旋转一圈，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害，同时在地面挑起3道扩散的荆棘，触碰造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%,30%,15%,6%</span><span>伤害。容易在普攻后施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
