				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="429" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">星锥：2单位特化盾，2次攻击或1次重击可破坏，每处涡眼有三枚星锥。</p>
			</content>
